    "name": "Reality Drift",
    "steam_appid": 3078120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/dcd112a9ce0ba41c674b33122f504596.avif?t=1763218123\" width=272 height=64 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭一系列奇异的世界，竞速并努力成为第一个将包裹送给讨厌的类神生物们的人——哪怕他们对你充满轻蔑与鄙夷。在每条赛道结束时，从三条新赛道中选择一条——你会如何决定，取决于你当前的属性和每条赛道对应的升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/becc567410f61f5588f9b7628e2783cb.poster.avif?t=1763218123\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/becc567410f61f5588f9b7628e2783cb.webm?t=1763218123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/becc567410f61f5588f9b7628e2783cb.mp4?t=1763218123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/679c242e00617964efd6171d45425a02.avif?t=1763218123\" width=272 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在每场竞速开始时拥有固定的加速、最大速度与抓地力属性。每次在你选择下一条赛道时，每个选项都会提供相应的属性升级。某些组合可能会彼此有连携效果，或是与你现有的属性合拍！也有些时候，你可能会见到一些额外的升级，例如助推、刹车充能、护盾或是反重力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/115862b6e2d4a7ba2ad7b00c3a92c715.avif?t=1763218123\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/c75edea186eb99f76dc240b3d475ea97.avif?t=1763218123\" width=402 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《现实漂移》中获胜，不仅需要高超的车技，也需要你做出正确的选择。你是会全力冲击加速与最大速度，还是会选择抓地力的构筑来让自己永远都不需要慢下来？选择需要实时做出，所以你只有几秒钟的时间来做决定！电脑控制的车辆也都遵循和你一样的规则，会选择自身获得的升级，但只有你可以选择下一条赛道是什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些任务包括Roguelike牌组构建玩法，你将有一副效果各异的牌组，在抽到时就会发挥作用。除了升级你车辆的核心属性外，你还会需要选择新的卡牌来加入你的牌组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/20b80cc8734256d44191a6b51a5df5f0.poster.avif?t=1763218123\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/20b80cc8734256d44191a6b51a5df5f0.webm?t=1763218123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/20b80cc8734256d44191a6b51a5df5f0.mp4?t=1763218123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你在比赛中获胜，你将解锁共计25个任务，每个任务都有独特的不同。赢下所有比赛将会解锁新游戏+模式，难度将进一步提示，考验你是否真正精通了这款游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/96308d86cd707c8010eec7b944904135.poster.avif?t=1763218123\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/96308d86cd707c8010eec7b944904135.webm?t=1763218123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078120/extras/96308d86cd707c8010eec7b944904135.mp4?t=1763218123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
